data.description: Perfectly situated on a corner lot in the prestigious Hermoso El Sol neighborhood, this home offers 4 beds and 2 baths. With paid off Solar Panels, you will enjoy the benefits of a low electric bill. It features vinyl plank wood flooring, a ship-lap corner fireplace, vaulted ceilings, and a soothing blue color scheme. The kitchen is both functional and stylish with tile countertops, ample cabinet space, an eat-in kitchen, and stainless steel appliances. The split floor plan provides privacy for the primary suite, which includes tray ceilings, recessed lighting, a spa-like bath with double sinks, a jet tub, and a spacious walk-in closet. The 4th bedroom can double as an office or bedroom with double doors. Additionally, there is RV parking on the side of the house, a 2 car garage, and refrigerated air for your comfort. This home offers a perfect blend of style and convenience in a highly desirable neighborhood. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours. Check out the 3D tour today!
